Grid Gap.code:
/*The distance between rows is 20px*/
/*The distance between columns is 10px*/
#grid-container {
    display: grid;
    grid-gap: 20px 10px;
}

Justify Items.code:
#container {
    display: grid;
    justify-items: center;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    grid-template-rows: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    grid-gap: 10px;
}

CSS grid-template-areas.code:
.item {
    grid-area: nav;
}
.grid-container {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-areas:
    'nav nav . .'
    'nav nav . .';
}

Justify Self.code:
#grid-container {
    display: grid;
    justify-items: start;
}

.grid-items {
    justify-self: end;
}

Align Items.code:
#container {
    display: grid;
    align-items: start;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    grid-template-rows: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    grid-gap: 10px;
}

カウンターの使用 - 基本.code:
body { counter-reset: section; }

h3::before {
  counter-increment: section; 
  content: "Section." counter(section);
}

カウンターの使用 - ネスト.code:
ol {
  counter-reset: section;   
  list-marker-type: none;
}

li::before {
  counter-increment: section;
  content: counters(section, ".") " "; 
}
